#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:574
msgid ""
"By default, the `ls` command does not display the last slash of a folder.  "
"In some cases, like for scripts for example, it is useful to display them:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:579
msgid "```bash $ ls -dF /etc /etc/ ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: docs/books/admin_guide/03-commands.md:581
msgid "Hide some extensions:"
